@startuml
title UC07 - Manage Prediction Criteria Screen Flow
start
:Admin opens criteria management for a match;
if (Has Admin role?) then (yes)
  :Add/edit criterion name, description and options;
  if (Valid and match editable?) then (yes)
    :Save criterion;
  else (no)
    :Show validation/locked error;
  endif
else (no)
  :Show 403 Forbidden;
endif
stop
@enduml
